lutions/articles/155000002288-getting-started-with-workflows) - [Copy.ai for High-Ticket Offers](https://www.copy.ai/) - [Selling to Affluent Audiences](https://www.selectadvisorsinstitute.com/our-perspective/affluent-marketing-ideas) - [Luxury Sales Page Templates](https://unbounce.com/ecommerce/how-to-sell-digital-products/) --- ### **Would you like me to begin indexing both playlists and start with the offer generator SOP, or is there a phase you want to tackle first?** *Once you confirm, I’ll post the first batch of indexed video summaries and the initial SOP table, then move to asset creation and workflow design.* --- **Let’s build your high-conversion, high-ticket, fully-automated digital product sales system—no sales calls required!** claude-4-sonnet I can't directly access YouTube playlists or videos to analyze their content. However, I can create a comprehensive framework for organizing Jeremy Haynes' content into a streamlined SOP for selling to affluent buyers without sales calls. Let me create a complete product launch template optimized for the top 10% earners in the US: ## **Knowledge Base Document: Affluent Digital Product Launch System** ### **Executive Summary** This system transforms video content into a fully automated sales funnel targeting high-net-worth individuals, eliminating the need for sales calls while maximizing conversion rates through AI-powered automation and premium positioning. ### **Phase 1: Content Analysis & Organization Framework** **Step-by-Step Video Content Extraction Process:** | Step | Action | Tool/Method | Expected Input | Expected Output | Timeline | |------|--------|-------------|----------------|-----------------|----------| | 1 | Video Transcription | Rev.com or Otter.ai | YouTube URLs | Complete transcripts with timestamps | 24-48 hours | | 2 | Content Categorization | Claude AI + Manual Review | Raw transcripts | Organized modules by topic | 2-3 hours | | 3 | Framework Extraction | AI Analysis | Categorized content 